# Chat Module

## Overview

Chat-First Gate Approval with Smart Secretary

## Goals

- **G1** — Chat-First Gate Approval with Smart Secretary
- **G2** — Inline GateCard renders diff view with Approve/Reject/Edit
- **G3** — SecretaryMessage delivers cross-session gates without blocking input
- **G4** — Gate queue enforces one-at-a-time delivery with snooze and dismiss
- **G5** — Ambient progress indicators keep chat history free of status spam
- **G6** — @Mention Agent Targeting directs chat messages to named agents with sticky profession routing
- *...and 3 more*

## Key Architecture Decisions

- **A1** — Chat Ephemeral Chrome Architecture
- **A2** — Chat-Turn Agent Handoff Architecture
- **A3** — Streaming Content Renderer Architecture

## Key Designs

- **D1** — GateCard & SecretaryMessage Components
- **D2** — ReportCard (Chat Terminal)
- **D3** — bring_in Tool & Chat Handoff
- **D4** — Streaming Content Renderer & Document Parser

